{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he-- he obviously had a lot of friends who were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean, like-- like I have a lot of non-Jewish friends here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if something happened in Bellevue Hill, maybe I could go next door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have friends and so on who, because of our previous friendship, would try and help us, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that he had a lot of friends, and he organized the escape.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, they may have done it for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know that one of the reasons they did it for was for money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that doesn't matter anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At least he was able to organize it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now they also-- a lot of them took money and spill-- spilled the beans to the-- to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you have to be pretty careful whom you're going to trust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the others helped you to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were risking their lives as well, of course, you understand, so you can see it from their point of view as well, because if they were caught, they risked their lives as well.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, some people are willing to risk things for lots of money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You've got to remember, these people were very poor, and the Jews were relatively well off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, they were the businessmen and the educated people in a small village like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had, you know-- they had possessions, obviously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so you had to find the right person to-- to help you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took a risk, and it was easier to take the money and become an informant of the Gestapo than to take the money and try and let you escape.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
